title: Dunstable Coffee Table
description: Anchor your seating ensemble in cottage-chic style with this coffee table. Crafted of rubberwood solids with pine veneers in a tastefully-distressed finish, the tabletop strikes a rectangular silhouette featuring planked details and moulded edges. Sporting a weathered white wash, this table’s base includes one open shelf for displaying coffee table books or fanning out issues of your favourite magazines, while hidden wheels make it easy to move the table for parties and events. Measures 19"

title: Arsenault Coffee Table
description: Crafted of manufactured wood with durable laminate veneers in a rustic Barnwood finish, this Arsenault Coffee Table strikes a two-tier rectangular silhouette on four chunky square legs, while black metal corner caps and X-frame stretchers offer added character and charm. Its lower shelf is great for fanning out issues of your favourite magazines, while the top surface provides a perfect platform for coasters and remotes. This coffee table has 100 lbs of weight capacity.

title: Laguna Coffee Table with Storage
description: Is the seating ensemble feeling empty? Not only do they anchor your space, but they offer room to stage a display and serve up trays of treats when you find yourself entertaining. This one, for example, exemplary of industrial style, it pairs rustic pine wood in your choice of 5 finishes, with metal elements for factory-chic contrast that works well in converted lofts and modern farmhouses alike. It also includes an open shelf for extra storage.

title: Tilden Lift Top 4 legs Coffee Table with Storage
description: Never leave your couch again. Give your home a classic new look with this vintage-looking lift-top coffee table from the Cannery Bridge® collection. This one-of-a-kind living room coffee table offers a spacious top surface that lifts up and forwards to create a multipurpose workspace for you to work from home, surf the web on your laptop or eat a yummy dinner all while relaxing from the comfort of your couch or loveseat. Beneath its handy lift-top surface is hidden storage for you to stow away any around-home essentials – spare blankets, board games, your collection of books, and any other items you typically wouldn't want your guests to see. This coffee table with storage also features open shelving for additional storage or to display home décor items like picture frames and knick-knacks. This beautiful coffee table with a lift top is finished on all sides in Lintel Oak®, making it the perfect versatile addition to any room in your home.

title: Chantrell Lift Top 4 Legs Coffee Table with Storage
description: Is your couch too comfy to leave but you still have work to get done? We have a solution for you. Check out this lift-top coffee table from the Carson Forge® collection. The top lifts up and forward creating a multipurpose work surface so you can work, browse online or eat dinner while relaxing on your couch. Beneath the top surface of this pop up coffee table is a hidden storage area that is ideal for storing items like blankets and your favourite books. The lower open shelf provides you with even more space to store and display things like organizing bins, board games and knick-knacks. This storage coffee table is finished on all sides for versatile placement throughout your home. This wood coffee table is finished on all sides in Coffee Oak® and paired with wrought iron style accents, making it the perfect statement piece in any room.

title: Marion Coffee Table with Storage
description: Pairing elegant and vintage details, this coffee table makes an eye-catching pick for your living room. It’s crafted from a blend of solid and engineered wood, and features a two-tone white and brown finish with gentle distressing for antiqued appeal. Up top, two decorative, carved tiles sit underneath a glass panel for a French country touch. Down below, two drawers and a slatted shelf provide plenty of storage for a few decks of cards and your favourite coffee table books.

title: Gossman Coffee Table with Storage
description: Rustic style meets eco-chic sensibility with this reclaimed wood coffee table, featuring a natural wood finish and concealed storage. Set it in the den to round out a bohemian ensemble, then top it with intriguing objets d'art and a lush succulent for an eclectic look.

title: Emiliano Lift Top Coffee Table with Storage
description: Double up on form and function with this square coffee table. Its dual lid tabletop provides easy access to the roomy space. Crafted with solid pine wood treated to a weathered grey finish, this generously scaled coffee table is rustic farmhouse living at its best.

title: Darian Coffee Table with Storage
description: Sporting a two-tone finish, dual-sided lid design and expansive storage space, this square coffee table takes the art of rustic farmhouse living to a new level. Designer touches include plank-effect styling, heavy distressing and industrial bracket hardware.
